Welcome to my technical portfolio!

This repository brings together the technical projects I have developed throughout my academic journey and extracurricular experiences. Each project reflects my continuous learning process and demonstrates how I apply statistics, mathematics, programming, and data analysis to solve real-world problems.

The portfolio includes case studies from different domains, showcasing the complete analytical workflow—from data exploration and statistical modeling to visualization, interpretation, and business-oriented recommendations.

As I continue learning, this repository will grow with new projects, methodologies, and applications.
